  "text": "With R141b, the maximum additional power output generated by the ORC is [CITATION_1] As the results presented in Figure 17 show, ethanol produces the highest power output for both cases. For Case B (heat source temperature of 49.73 °C) and minimum temperature on 2 °C, one bottoming ORC would provide additional 45 MW power output (90 MW total, or 15% of the current plant output). At the same minimum temperature, the additional power output for Case A would be 36 MW (72 MW total).",
